text: I’ve had the chicken cutlet burger and the chicken quesadilla so far and enjoyed it. For me, the quesadilla was not enough food to equate one meal, so next time I will add other things to it. This resto is the kind where u get a buzzer and you pick your food up when it’s ready, so expect to wait a little bit for your food. I’ve only gone around dinner time when there’s no crowd and only takes about 5 minutes.
Nice place, neon lighta deco and good food for the night!
